Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:03.38,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A racing second hand, a shooting comet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.38,0:00:06.98,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Let's heal hearts dried by modern society with Conan's logic!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.98,0:00:10.62,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Today's case has Ran{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-neechan{\r\be10} playing an important part!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.62,0:00:12.32,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:14.39,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.39,0:00:16.93,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.44,0:01:40.34,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Ran, the old man, and I attended the Izu Mystery Tour
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.34,0:01:46.14,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}in place of Dr. Agasa, his friend, and his friend's granddaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.48,0:01:51.75,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The anonymous tour organizer would play the Night Baron
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:54.02,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and cause an incident during the tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.02,0:01:59.83,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Whoever determines the organizer's identity gets to stay for free
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.83,0:02:03.66,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and receives floppy disks containing a certain program.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.63,0:02:07.50,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The attendees keep each other in check...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.50,0:02:11.23,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The Night Baron pushed me off a balcony when I was all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.51,0:02:14.53,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I fell into a pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.14,0:02:18.74,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Was this a warning? Or just part of the game?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.98,0:02:22.38,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}And then it happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:26.28,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The Night Baron plummeted onto a bronze statue!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:36.03,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Izu Princess Hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.29,0:02:38.25,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A person wearing a mask?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.13,0:02:50.09,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Like I thought, it {\i1}was{\i0} the Night Baron who fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.22,0:02:54.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:58.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.02,0:02:59.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:05.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Don't you live\Nwith Detective Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.44,0:03:07.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! You know better!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.78,0:03:10.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:11.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it isn't Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.74,0:03:13.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:17.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you Yokomizo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} from the\NSaitama police department?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.16,0:03:18.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:19.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:23.82,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Yokomizo\NTransferred to Shizuoka Police Department
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:24.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I transferred to Shizuoka last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:26.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:27.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:31.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ebara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.41,0:03:34.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.01,0:03:35.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.10,0:03:38.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was on the same\NMystery Tour as us...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:39.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystery Tour?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:44.02,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He only has one glove on...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:49.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:54.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So the goal is to figure out who\Nthe organizer and Night Baron is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:58.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means the organizer\Nwas Ebara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.31,0:04:05.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A suicide? An accident? Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.09,0:04:09.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, where is Detective Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.02,0:04:10.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:12.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the pub on the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.34,0:04:13.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:16.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:19.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's go talk to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:20.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Come on, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:21.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:22.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:26.98,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10\fad(200,200)}Tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:33.27,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Hotel 2F\NPub "Emerald"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.38,0:04:37.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a time for Dad to get plastered!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.58,0:04:41.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:46.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Ebara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} fell off\Ndressed as the Night Baron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:52.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, according to eyewitnesses,\Nhe fell at precisely 10 PM!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:54.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:56.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your breath...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:04:59.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,10 PM, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.81,0:05:00.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.56,0:05:03.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! It's this late already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:08.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, did you check Room 2101,\Nwhere he was staying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:12.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We tried to, but we\Ncouldn't get inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.11,0:05:20.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A security lock on the inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.49,0:05:21.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.61,0:05:34.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! We're in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:39.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are clothes here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:42.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the ones\Nhe was wearing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:45.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He even left his room key here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.56,0:05:50.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,\Nhe {\i1}was{\i0} pretty drunk...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.67,0:05:54.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The window's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.44,0:05:57.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's a balcony outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:04.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It would appear this\Nis where he fell from.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:07.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Careful, Detective Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.57,0:06:11.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This was just a simple accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:13.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,An accident?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:17.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt about it.\NThere's a glove in the railing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:18.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.14,0:06:24.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably tried to climb down\Nthe balcony in that costume
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:27.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to scare the attendee\Nin the room below.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:31.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But he screwed up\Nand fell to his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.11,0:06:32.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.32,0:06:35.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the 21st floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:38.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Would he really try to\Ngo down without a rope?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:41.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, the key was inside the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:46.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If he did make it to the room\Nbelow and then left through it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:49.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he would've needed the\Nkey to get back in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.73,0:06:52.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.12,0:06:58.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My pen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,0:07:02.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let me have\Na look at the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:03.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:06.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing it won't\Nchange anything, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.83,0:07:14.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.22,0:07:19.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So he fell 21 stories\Nonto that statue...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:22.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Has anyone gotten near the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.09,0:07:26.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, sir. Aside from us, only one\Nother person has touched him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:28.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That little boy there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:31.62,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That brat again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:37.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:41.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find the pen\Nthat I dropped...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.88,0:07:46.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that Ebara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was\Nthe one who fell, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:50.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No question about it.\NIt was Tokio Ebara.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.59,0:07:53.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And he had a mask on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:55.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A mask?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:08:01.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So he was the tour\Norganizer and the Night Baron.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:05.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it. I always\Nthought he was suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off. This isn't the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:14.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it is disturbing that the\Nimmortal Night Baron would perish...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:16.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.73,0:08:19.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Members of the same tour I'm on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.58,0:08:21.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But why would Ebara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:24.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.25,0:08:25.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,An accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:29.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He fell off the balcony\Ntrying to scare you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:34.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate,\Nthe Night Baron has died.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:37.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the tour is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:42.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:46.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird. What's with this necktie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.44,0:08:49.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the knot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:51.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The knot?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:54.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's backwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:57.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But this could be normal for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:09:00.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a necktie of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:00.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:04.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you get that necktie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:07.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A waitress gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.11,0:09:09.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She said he forgot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:12.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true! This tie's knot is normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:13.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.70,0:09:15.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Is there something else?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.43,0:09:18.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's wearing his belt weird, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:20.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See? It's upside-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:22.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not good with\Naccessories, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:25.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is very strange, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:28.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He didn't put these clothes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:30.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone put them on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:35.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means Ebara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was\Npushed off the 21st floor
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.68,0:09:38.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,by the real Night Baron.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:43.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the homicidal\NNight Baron is still among us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.08,0:09:52.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears we must ask\Nwhere each of you were
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.20,0:09:55.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when Ebara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} fell at 10 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.70,0:09:59.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to the front desk and ask them to prepare a room for questioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:00.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.54,0:10:02.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do with the body and the costume?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:04.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:08.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's set him in the office until we're done with the questioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:10.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.06,0:10:12.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.98,0:10:12.94,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,INTERROGATION ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.98,0:10:12.94,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,AUTHORIZED PERSONNEL ONLY
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.98,0:10:12.94,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,SHIZUOKA POLICE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:11.60,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,INTERROGATION ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:11.60,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,AUTHORIZED PERSONNEL ONLY
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:11.60,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,SHIZUOKA POLICE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:17.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, at 10 PM you were in the observation\Nlounge with Ran and Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.40,0:10:21.49,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru Maeda (30)\NJonan University Electrical Engineering Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.40,0:10:22.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I left them some time after 10 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.82,0:10:24.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.74,0:10:28.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But {\i1}you{\i0} were the one who\Nlooked at the time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:31.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:34.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. Call in the next person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:39.01,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideko Kamijo (29)\NSoftware Company CEO
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:37.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My alibi's airtight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:42.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I was in the pub with him the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:44.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Mr. Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:46.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.97,0:10:50.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But didn't he get dead-drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:53.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:54.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:57.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We were in an open-air restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:11:00.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,near where Ebara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:59.49,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen'ichiro Kaneshiro (74)\NComputer Company Owner
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:03.07,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizue Hayashi (56)\NKaneshiro's Butler
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:01.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Shizue{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:03.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:05.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can anyone vouch for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.49,0:11:12.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was such a commotion that\NI'm unsure people would remember us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:17.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But with the way he died,\NI can't say I blame them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:22.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring in the next one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:28.93,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro Kon'no (28)\NBank Employee
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:26.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in my room reading my e-mail
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:29.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,from 9:45 until after 10 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:33.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The hotel's records should prove that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:36.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you didn't speak\Nwith anyone, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:41.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I did. With my computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:42.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:45.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Call in the next person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:47.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were alone in your room, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:50.96,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko Sayama (24)\NHigh School Math Teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:48.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.79,0:11:51.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was watching TV alone
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:53.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,until Satoru returned after 10 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:11:57.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I take it you have\Nnobody to vouch for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:12:00.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can describe what the\Nmovie was about, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:02.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a bomb in a skyscraper...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:06.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. That won't work as proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:15.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe they\Nmade me guard him alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:18.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they finish\Ntheir questioning soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:23.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That detective and your\Nfather really tick me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:25.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet they think I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:27.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:30.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's tons of other\Nsuspicious people!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:31.37,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10\fad(0,500)}Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:35.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is my shift over?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:38.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:45.16,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Everyone on the tour\Nhas a flimsy alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:49.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you maybe order room service\Nwhen you were in your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:52.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've already said so if I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:58.50,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}How did the killer leave after\Npushing Ebara{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} off his balcony?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:13:02.53,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The room had its security lock set!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:08.87,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}All we know is that the\Nkiller is still in the hotel...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:11.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You called the front desk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:14.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I asked for a wake-up call.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:15.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:18.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,About 10 PM, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:22.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The hotel keeps records of\Nwhen calls are made from rooms!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:26.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That means your alibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:29.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Akiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:37.86,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10\fad(200,200)}The Night Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.14,0:13:45.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Night Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:48.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:50.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:04.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:08.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?!\NHe's getting away! Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:09.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:11.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! He showed up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:15.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the heck didn't you catch him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:17.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I was in shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:19.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Yokomizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.22,0:14:20.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:22.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was collapsed in the\Nroom with the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:25.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears he was hit by someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.02,0:14:26.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! And the body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:30.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, but the Night\NBaron costume is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.99,0:14:32.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Night Baron costume?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:33.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:34.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Yokomizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:35.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:37.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Night Baron's in the pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:38.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:44.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The mask, hat, wig, and cape!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:47.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So what about the one wearing it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:49.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could he or she be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:53.59,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Probably up there.\NIt was tossed from that balcony.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:57.10,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Why did the killer show\Nup at the elevators{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:15:01.04,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}If they needed to go up, they would've\Nused the stairs to go unseen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:04.79,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}And why did they have\Nto wear the costume,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.79,0:15:07.69,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}not to mention risk being\Ncaught trying to steal it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.69,0:15:09.72,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His methods are too aggressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:13.01,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Could these latest things\Nhave been unplanned?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:15.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! We need to re-question them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:17.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Round up all the suspects!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.70,0:15:18.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.74,0:15:23.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were all in your rooms,\Nand you have no witnesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:25.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means none of you\Nhave alibis for when
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:29.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and the others\Nwere attacked! Correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:32.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.05,0:15:37.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You told us not to leave our rooms,\Nand that's just what we did!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:40.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We only did as you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:43.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not stupid enough\Nto ignore the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:45.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:48.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Maeda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nshare the same room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:51.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't check if\Nthey were there or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:52.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no time to!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.42,0:15:56.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We all came right away to\Nreport about the Night Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:57.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.57,0:15:59.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:03.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, we'll need\Nto check all your rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:05.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yours first, Maeda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:06.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:13.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing seems out of the ordinary...\NWhat the...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.92,0:16:15.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:17.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just letting some air in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:21.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That stupid kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:23.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just to be sure,\Nplease empty your pockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:26.89,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I have this room's\Nlayout figured out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:30.01,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Ebara{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} fell\Nfrom that balcony...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:34.80,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yes. The killer dressed\Nhim up as the Night Baron
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:37.16,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and pushed him off to make\Nit look like an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:42.62,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But the security lock was set\Nin the room where it happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.62,0:16:47.14,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}In other words, the killer didn't\Nleave through the door afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.78,0:16:50.19,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Meaning this was a locked-room murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:55.24,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The balcony is the only other way out of the room...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:58.40,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But going from there into\Nthis room is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:17:00.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's this medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:02.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ordinary sleeping pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:06.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I always carry them with me for\Nmy insomnia. That a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:08.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I see?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:10.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go to the next room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:16.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't find anything, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:18.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just making sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:22.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.07,0:17:25.73,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The balcony he fell from\Nis directly above...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:28.00,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It might be possible\Nto climb down here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:30.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you keep following me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:34.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd watch your great\Ndetective skills in action!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:38.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay! In that case,\Npay close attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.51,0:17:40.87,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}There are no signs of\Nthe window being broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:43.33,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Guess he can be cute sometimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:46.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was this window always locked, Mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:51.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes are bad.\NCan you answer, Shizue{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:55.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it was. I check\Nit each time we leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:58.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kon'no{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s room is next.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:04.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that he was suspected\Nof using his bank's computers
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:07.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,without permission\Nand was thus demoted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:11.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He may have wanted to see\Nthe Baron the most of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:12.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.56,0:18:15.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's simply a rumor, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.46,0:18:17.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that old man told you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.59,0:18:19.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:24.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's he to talk? He's the one who\Nhates the Night Baron the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:25.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.51,0:18:32.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, the son he so dutifully\Nraised was murdered by the virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:35.75,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Come to think of it,\Nhe did mention that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.75,0:18:39.38,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The Night Baron. Hearing that\Nname brings back memories
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:42.61,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}of my son who died four years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.61,0:18:45.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A virus? His son died of an illness?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:47.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that have to do\Nwith the Night Baron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:49.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good question...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.94,0:18:51.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you playing dumb?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.08,0:18:52.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.62,0:18:56.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop! I'll give you\Nsome special information!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:19:01.07,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This is the closest window to the balcony,\Nbut there's no way across.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:02.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With Kamijo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:06.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They were married.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.01,0:19:09.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I hear they\Ndivorced three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.47,0:19:14.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. The late\NTokio Ebara was my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:19.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was three years ago...\Nwhen I learned he was a hacker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:20.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hacker?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:24.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A criminal who steals computer data!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.32,0:19:28.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who uses a\Ncomputer loathes hackers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:32.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm relieved that he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:33.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:39.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe Akiko Sayama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s brother\Nran a small software company.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:43.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means she's no exception, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:48.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning that everyone on the\Ntour had a reason to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:50.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:55.29,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh? These are the same\Npills that Akiko{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} had...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:57.09,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Are these also—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:19:59.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what are these pills for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.71,0:20:03.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't touch my things!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:04.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it cold medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:06.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.24,0:20:09.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I thought they were\Nsleeping pills. Guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:11.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.12,0:20:16.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you blabbing about now?!\NGo get in bed, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:20.42,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I didn't check the room's layout yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.59,0:20:27.20,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Ah, well. It's the same layout\Nas Kon'no{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s room downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:30.98,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Well, looking at\Neveryone's rooms, we get...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.98,0:20:37.48,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Room 2101\NEbara
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.77,0:20:37.48,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Room 2102\NKamijo
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:37.48,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Room 2001\NKaneshiro & Hayashi
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.77,0:20:37.48,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Room 2002\NKonno
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:37.48,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Room 1901\NMaeda & Sayama
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.77,0:20:37.48,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Body
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.16,0:20:37.48,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}...as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:41.26,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}So the only possible escape\Nfrom Ebara{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s balcony
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:43.76,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}was through Kaneshiro{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}\N{\i0}and Hayashi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s room...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:45.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do we do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:49.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure. It's a piece\Nof the security lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.24,0:20:51.99,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh, right. Ebara{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s room\Nis on this floor, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.99,0:20:54.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there's something on the tip...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.49,0:20:56.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cellophane tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:20:59.51,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Wait a minute! Could this be—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.54,0:22:31.56,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He dodged all of my kicks\Nwith no effort at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.56,0:22:39.57,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}And only one of the suspects could've done that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.57,0:22:41.53,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.53,0:22:44.56,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Tell me, Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.56,0:22:46.50,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.21,0:22:50.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Open up, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.21,0:22:52.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.90,0:22:54.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The security lock was set.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.99,0:22:58.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange. I don't\Nremember locking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.45,0:22:59.74,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Success!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.74,0:23:01.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.60,0:23:04.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Some tears came out when I yawned.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.62,0:23:07.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm leaving for a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.46,0:23:08.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This late?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.19,0:23:09.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.67,0:23:12.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.96,0:23:15.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kids shouldn't be awake this late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.43,0:23:17.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.26,0:23:20.71,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Using that trick, anyone\Ncould have killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.71,0:23:23.17,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'll have to check\Neach of their alibis...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.17,0:23:25.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you hear about Misawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.79,0:23:29.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,About how the killer knocked him\Nout in the office with the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.11,0:23:32.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't Misawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} a karate expert?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.07,0:23:34.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Best in the department!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.95,0:23:38.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he {\i1}was{\i0} caught off guard...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:39.99,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Hey, hey, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.99,0:23:42.69,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10\fad(0,300)}Could the killer be...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.05,0:23:49.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.72,0:23:52.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, who set the security lock?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.12,0:23:54.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I locked it from the outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.09,0:23:57.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.93,0:24:01.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That would seal the room and make it look like an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.80,0:24:05.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I found an alibi for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.30,0:24:06.87,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.87,0:24:09.20,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}There's one place where the wind is—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.20,0:24:15.20,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.20,0:24:20.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint: Wind through the buildings
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.89,0:24:22.51,Dialogue Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, the case is closed next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.51,0:24:23.67,Dialogue Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.67,0:24:24.90,Dialogue Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Me again?!
